'''Online Tools for a Sustainable Collaborative Economy'''


URL = http://open.coop/tiki-download_wiki_attachment.php?attId=18



=Description=


"This paper looks at the theory and practice of online systems aimed at building an economy based upon trust. It looks at practical ways in which we can create an economy driven directly by social and economic need rather than commercial pressures. It describes current projects which are developing some of the needed tools. It gives an extended fictional example in which these tools are integrated and extended, and provides a summary of the theoretical principles upon which such a sustainable, collaborative economy would need to be based."



